tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE orders ( 
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
  product_id INT, 
  supplier_id INT, 
  order_date DATE, 
  quantity INT 
);

CREATE TABLE InventoryLevel (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
product_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
quantity INT NOT NULL,
location VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
last_updated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL)
